Add command line tools to the path:
- By adding command folders to your system path,
  it'll make a lot easier to do things from the command line when you want
  to see exactly what's happening in the background.
- The Android SDK tools is generally used from Android Studio
- But the SDK tools is also used from Command Lines
- Add the following two folder to the System PATH environment
  android_sdk/platform-tools
  android_sdk/platform-tools/tools
- adb Commands:
  adb
  adb devices
